HEADWORD: Synodist
<hw>Syn"od*ist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An adherent to a
synod.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>These <qex>synodists</qex> thought fit in Latin as yet to veil
their decrees from vulgar eyes.</q> <rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Synoecious</ent>⟦br⟧
